sven andrighetto (born march 21, 1993) is a swiss ice hockey winger currently playing with the montreal canadiens of the national hockey league (nhl). the canadiens selected him in the 3rd round (86th overall) of the 2013 nhl entry draft, his last year of eligibility. he previously played with the rouyn-noranda huskies of the quebec major junior hockey league, with whom he would finish sixth in scoring in 2012â€“13.